line_1: Be left to grace thy fretted rump.

line_1: Converted now into a real Rump,
line_2: Sliced off the slaughter'd Monster's quondam stump,

line_1: So while little TABBY was washing her Rump,
line_2: The Ladies kept drinking it out of a Pump.
